//axhos_step
. *Assert sshd_config Match block routes workload to absolute-path authkeys*:
.. {busc_call}
PowerShell `Get-Content ($env:ProgramData + '\ssh\sshd_config') -Raw` over `«ADMIN_SESSION»`
.. {busc_store}
`«SSHD_CONFIG_RAW»`
.. {busc_require}
`«SSHD_CONFIG_RAW»` contains a `Match User ${BUJB_workload_user}` header
whose next non-blank line is `AuthorizedKeysFile
__PROGRAMDATA__/ssh/users/${BUJB_workload_user}/authorized_keys`
(indentation tolerated; sshd accepts indented continuations)
.. {busc_fatal}
on absence or mismatch -- {bust_caparison_windows} scope (Phase 1 SSH-trust
hardening). Workload SSH auth depends on this block: without it, sshd
falls back to the workload's profile-relative `authorized_keys` path and
exposes the demotion failure mode that absolute-path Match defends against.

//axhos_step
. *Assert workload authkeys directory present*:
.. {busc_call}
PowerShell `Test-Path ($env:ProgramData + '\ssh\users\${BUJB_workload_user}')` over `«ADMIN_SESSION»`
.. {busc_store}
`«AUTHKEYS_DIR_PRESENT»`
.. {busc_require}
`«AUTHKEYS_DIR_PRESENT»` equals `True`
.. {busc_fatal}
on `False` or transport failure -- {bust_caparison_windows} scope (Phase
1). {busn_garrison} on `w` writes the bare workload authkeys file into
this directory and the lockdown rewrite overwrites it; absence here
guarantees garrison-w fails at place-bare-trust with `DirectoryNotFoundException`.

//axhos_step
. *Assert workload authkeys directory ACL = admins+SYSTEM only*:
.. {busc_call}
PowerShell `icacls ($env:ProgramData + '\ssh\users\${BUJB_workload_user}')` over `«ADMIN_SESSION»`
.. {busc_store}
`«AUTHKEYS_DIR_ACL»`
.. {busc_require}
`«AUTHKEYS_DIR_ACL»` lists both `BUILTIN\Administrators` and `NT AUTHORITY\SYSTEM`
as Full-Control principals AND contains none of `BUILTIN\Users`,
`Authenticated Users`, or `${BUJB_workload_user}` (sshd reads as NT
AUTHORITY\SYSTEM and does not need workload-side grants; parallel to
`administrators_authorized_keys`'s admins+SYSTEM-only ACL discipline).
.. {busc_fatal}
on missing required principal or forbidden principal present --
{bust_caparison_windows} scope (Phase 1 icacls
`/inheritance:r /grant SYSTEM:F /grant BUILTIN\Administrators:F`).

//axhos_step
. *Assert Tailscale service StartupType*:
.. {busc_call}
PowerShell `Get-Service Tailscale | Select-Object StartType`
.. {busc_store}
`«SVC_STARTTYPE»`
.. {busc_require}
`«SVC_STARTTYPE»` equals `Automatic`
.. {busc_fatal}
on mismatch -- {bust_caparison_windows} scope

